Cloud Native Resource Monitoring App Using K8s

# Monitoring Application in Python with Docker and Kubernetes

This project is a Python-based monitoring application built using Flask and `psutil`. It showcases a complete workflow, from local development to containerization with Docker, image management with AWS ECR, and deployment in a Kubernetes cluster on AWS EKS.

